        "sender_full_name": "Mario Carneiro",
        "timestamp": 1733949339
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I would guess you can get there by using:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A linear version of <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=Fin.append#doc\">docs#Fin.append</a></li>\n<li>A linear version of composition with <code>Fin.cast</code></li>\n</ul>",
        "id": 488188079,
